feat(auth)!: replace jsonwebtoken with jose for JWT handling

Migrate JWT signing and verification from jsonwebtoken to jose, which
provides better TypeScript support, standards compliance, and no native
dependencies.

Files changed:
- src/auth/jwt.ts
- src/auth/middleware.ts
- src/auth/types.ts
- package.json

BREAKING CHANGE: JWT tokens signed with jsonwebtoken are incompatible
with jose. All active sessions will be invalidated. Users must log in
again after deployment.

Refs: PROJ-189
